    public interface ChangeRecordType
extends utam.core.framework.base.RootPageObject
    Selector: forceChangeRecordType. Represents the force:changeRecordType Aura component. Get selectable ChangeRecordType radio buttons, get selected item message, tag line, record types, select record. Get count of top-down record types.
